  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下新产品的系统架构图。最前端是一个Next.js的UI层，我暂时叫它a-ui。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a-ui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，a-ui是用户直接面对的界面层。那它跟后端怎么交互？直接连数据库吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a-ui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不，它通过REST API调用一个独立的网关层，我们叫b-api。这样前后端解耦，也方便做统一认证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a-ui",
        "b-api",
        "REST API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上a-ui到b-api的REST API连接。那b-api后面直接是业务服务吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a-ui",
        "b-api",
        "REST API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，b-api会路由到两个微服务：一个是产品服务a-product-service，另一个是评价服务b-review-service。都用DTOs和OpenAPI规范做接口契约。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b-api",
        "a-product-service",
        "b-review-service",
        "DTOs",
        "OpenAPI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：b-api同时连到a-product-service和b-review-service，两条线都标注DTOs和OpenAPI，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b-api",
        "a-product-service",
        "b-review-service",
        "DTOs",
        "OpenAPI"
