    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。这两个服务共享一套核心逻辑，我打算抽象一个c-core模块，专门放公共的业务规则。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a-product-service",
        "b-review-service",
        "c-core",
        "Core Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，a-product-service和b-review-service都通过Core Logic连到c-core。那数据层怎么设计？",
      "elements_involved": [
